Gorgeous, easy, flattering – just a few of the words that describe our Jersey Wrap Top. A faux wrap features pleats and gathers at the side seams for a forgiving fit, while a deep V-neck shows off a little skin with beautiful, face-framing lines. Stretchy, yet compact, fabric means this style plays well with all bra types, so there's no second guessing your support. Speaking of fabric, our new signature cotton-modal jersey keeps it comfy all day, so you can opt for a classic look with our black colorway, or something a little more fun with our statement-making, ’60s-inspired Chain Link print.

FINAL SALE ITEM
We do not accept returns or exchanges on final sale items. Email us your bra, denim, and dress size (ex: 34C, 28, 6) to ensure you get the right size.

Fit & Sizing

Gabby wears a Size S in this top. She is 5'9" and typically wears a 2 in dresses.

Sizing Notes: This top is fitted and fits true to size.

View our size chart.

Material & Care

Material: 56% Cotton, 38% Modal, 6% Spandex

Product Care - Easy: Machine wash cold with like colors and tumble dry low or lay flat to dry. Do not bleach.
